## Development

### Setup

```bash
# Clone monorepo
git clone https://mercola-consulting-services.ghe.com/MCS/A2A-Protocol-AIS.git
cd A2A-Protocol-AIS/packages/python

# Install dependencies
pip install -e ".[dev]"

# Run tests
pytest

# Format code
black src tests
ruff check src tests

# Type check
mypy src
```

